          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-1" n="1">Beneath this verdant Hillock lies</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-2" n="2"><hi rend="large-writing">Demar</hi> the Wealthy and the Wise.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-3" n="3">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-4" n="4">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-5" n="5">His Heirs that he might safely rest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-6" n="6">Have put his Carcase in a <hi rend="large-writing">Chest</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-7" n="7">The very Chest, in which, they Say,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-8" n="8">His other Self, his <hi rend="large-writing">Money</hi>, lay.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-9" n="9">And if his Heirs Continue kind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-10" n="10">To that dear Self he left behind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-11" n="11">I dare believe, that four in five</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-265Y-line-12" n="12">Will think his <hi rend="large-writing">Better</hi> half Alive.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
